Wine dataset

This labelled dataset contains a quality score (0-10) and 11 chemical test results on the variety of Portuguese "Vino Verde" wine (Cortez et al., 2009.)

The first look of the data

  WhiteWine <- read.csv("winequality-white.csv",sep = ";")
  str(WhiteWine)
